    <section class="main" id="main">
        <div class="container my-5">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-4">
                    <div class="row mb-4">
                        <div class="col">
                            <div class="section-wrap">
                                <h2 class="text-center">Behold!</h2>
                                <h3 class="text-center">Your BMI value</h3>
                                <h1 class="text-center" id="bmiValue">22.9</h1>
                                <h6 class="text-center">based on your most recent record</h6>
                                <div class="d-flex flex-row align-items-center justify-content-between m-4" id="bmiBar">
                                    <div class="bar red-bar"></div>
                                    <div class="bar red-bar"></div>
                                    <div class="bar yellow-bar"></div>
                                    <div class="bar green-bar"></div>
                                    <div class="bar green-bar"></div>
                                    <div class="bar green-bar"></div>
                                    <div class="bar green-bar"></div>
                                    <div class="bar green-bar"></div>
                                    <div class="bar yellow-bar"></div>
                                    <div class="bar yellow-bar"></div>
                                    <div class="bar yellow-bar"></div>
                                    <div class="bar yellow-bar"></div>
                                    <div class="bar red-bar"></div>
                                    <div class="bar red-bar"></div>
                                    <div class="bar red-bar"></div>
                                    <div class="bar red-bar"></div>
                                    <div class="bar red-bar"></div>
                                    <div class="bar red-bar"></div>
                                </div>
                                <h4 class="text-center" id="bmiComment">Yup! You're healthy!</h4>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col">
                            <div class="section-wrap-yellow">
                                <div class="d-flex flex-row justify-content-around">
                                    <div>
                                        <h3 class="text-center">Height</h3>
                                        <div class="d-flex flex-row justify-content-center">
                                            <h2 id="height">175</h2>
                                            <h5 class="align-self-end measure">cm</h5>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <h3 class="text-center">Weight</h3>
                                        <div class="d-flex flex-row justify-content-center">
                                            <h2 id="weight">70</h2>
                                            <h5 class="align-self-end measure">kg</h5>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-8">
                    <div class="section-wrap" id="infoZone">
                        <h3>What's this?</h3>
                        <br>
                        <img src="./images/bmichart.png" alt="BMI Chart" style="width: 100%">
                        <p>BMI is a measurement of a person's leanness or corpulence based on their height and weight, and is intended to quantify tissue mass. It is widely used as a general indicator of whether a person has a healthy body weight for their height.</p>
                        <p>For adult, the classification for BMI values is listed below:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>BMI &lt; 18.5: Underweight</li>
                            <li>18.5 &le; BMI &lt; 25: Healthy</li>
                            <li>25 &le; BMI &lt; 30: Overweight</li>
                            <li>BMI &ge; 30: Obese</li>
                        </ul>
                        <h3>What does my BMI tell about me?</h3>
                        <br>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
